# Tier B vector tiles are large -> hosted on object storage, not committed.
/public/tiles

# NOTE: /public/geo and /public/data are GENERATED (npm run geo:build) but
# committed on purpose: they are small (<20 MB), required at runtime, and let
# the app deploy without the multi-GB raw static-data dump.

# typescript
*.tsbuildinfo
